  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a variety of islands with a red balloon!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a balloon as passionate as its color and press forward to achieve your goal. After choosing your direction, decide how far you want to send your balloon soaring. Join the journey of a balloon that transcends seas and mountains, reaching for the sky!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/0cc0a6447e9fb666b9c59e753214d668.poster.avif?t=1742828666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/0cc0a6447e9fb666b9c59e753214d668.webm?t=1742828666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/0cc0a6447e9fb666b9c59e753214d668.mp4?t=1742828666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An ode to the art of taking it slow.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While fast, exhilarating action is undoubtedly fun, there are times when taking it slow is necessary. Slow but sure. You might feel frustrated at times, but as a balloon, that’s just the way it is.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/735811bbc6346afe671fffc32f6c2106.poster.avif?t=1742828666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/735811bbc6346afe671fffc32f6c2106.webm?t=1742828666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/735811bbc6346afe671fffc32f6c2106.mp4?t=1742828666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >To reclaim your childlike spirit...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In intricate terrains and among unknown obstacles, dangers lurk at every corner, waiting for a chance to hinder you. You might find yourself blocked by obstacles and discouraged. But don’t worry! If you persistently move toward your destination, you will ultimately succeed. It’s time to reclaim the childlike spirit that believed you could do anything.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore a variety of islands with a red balloon!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Become a balloon as passionate as its color and press forward to achieve your goal. After choosing your direction, decide how far you want to send your balloon soaring. Join the journey of a balloon that transcends seas and mountains, reaching for the sky!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/0cc0a6447e9fb666b9c59e753214d668.poster.avif?t=1742828666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/0cc0a6447e9fb666b9c59e753214d668.webm?t=1742828666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/0cc0a6447e9fb666b9c59e753214d668.mp4?t=1742828666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >An ode to the art of taking it slow.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While fast, exhilarating action is undoubtedly fun, there are times when taking it slow is necessary. Slow but sure. You might feel frustrated at times, but as a balloon, that’s just the way it is.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/735811bbc6346afe671fffc32f6c2106.poster.avif?t=1742828666\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/735811bbc6346afe671fffc32f6c2106.webm?t=1742828666\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3516600/extras/735811bbc6346afe671fffc32f6c2106.mp4?t=1742828666\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >To reclaim your childlike spirit...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In intricate terrains and among unknown obstacles, dangers lurk at every corner, waiting for a chance to hinder you. You might find yourself blocked by obstacles and discouraged. But don’t worry! If you persistently move toward your destination, you will ultimately succeed. It’s time to reclaim the childlike spirit that believed you could do anything.</p>",
